cation":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.724952,"lng":-155.087041,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"","centerType":"fitness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Fitness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"80765d7c-cede-4f97-a4e4-51b433e26116","name":"Evry Collective HI","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c1a8a9_aae0eed467894be197a90c677287d6d9~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_2500,h_3739,al_c/c1a8a9_aae0eed467894be197a90c677287d6d9~mv2.jpg","modality":"Meditation, Yoga","modalities":["Meditation","Yoga"],"location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.723733,"lng":-155.085163,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Attend a Group Fitness Class, Buti, Sculpt, Barre, Pilates, Inferno Pilates, Hot Yoga, Heated Classes, Vinyasa, Private and one on one training in Hilo, Hawai'i at EVRY Collective HI.","centerType":"yoga_studio","centerTypeLabel":"Yoga Studio","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":["https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c1a8a9_aae0eed467894be197a90c677287d6d9~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_2500,h_3739,al_c/c1a8a9_aae0eed467894be197a90c677287d6d9~mv2.jpg"],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"e0f26e09-4395-4a66-8149-c100be18544f","name":"Fitness Forever Kailua-Kona","image":"","modality":"Yoga","modalities":["Yoga"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.643077,"lng":-155.99433,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Right in the heart of Kailua-Kona, Fitness Forever is where locals train, sweat, and grow together. From sunrise workouts to late-night lifts, our clean, open gym is built to move with you. Get your heart pumping with top-tier cardio and strength equipment, or drop into one of our high-energy group fitness classes.  \nMembers love our extras—like Fit 3D body scans, fast WiFi, secure lockers, and monthly challenges that keep things fun and motivating. Free parking makes it easy to come and go, but once you're here, you’ll want to stay awhile. Because in Kona, this is where Hawai‘i works out.","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"2e43e1a2-bc6e-485f-a466-9429bf239240","name":"Five Mountain Fitness Center Inc","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/93f780cd9e7d41929777baeed6ccc93e.jpg/v1/fill/w_288,h_192,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/93f780cd9e7d41929777baeed6ccc93e.jpg","modality":"Yoga","modalities":["Yoga"],"location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.022614,"lng":-155.674864,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"We pride ourselves in being a full service fitness center offering a clean and well-maintained atmosphere with a friendly and accommodating staff. At Five Mountain Fitness Center, it is about the one thing that matters the most, your health. People of all ages come to Five Mountain Fitness Center to exercise and improve their health. At Five Mountain Fitness Center, our three main goals are centered around the concepts of:","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"ae9e02bb-513f-46e5-a0f1-17819f1c7b2a","name":"Gingerhill Farm Retreat","image":"https://gingerhillfarm.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Homepage_Accommodations_Image1.png","modality":"Massage, Yoga, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Massage","Yoga","Nature Therapy"],"location":"Kealakekua","rating":5,"lat":19.50394,"lng":-155.926358,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Eat delicious, healing farm-to-fork food. Get intimate with nature and find your unadulterated self. We would love to see you at our Hawaii retreat.","centerType":"retreat_center","centerTypeLabel":"Retreat Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"30993473-5917-4c93-9a09-b7ed43a72fda","name":"Hawaiian Healing Yoga","image":"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/ef8d64b0-c42f-445b-bb33-0b500e83cff8/11c4a945a61091e61e5860f4f9296456.jpg","modality":"Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing, Naturopathic, Yoga","modalities":["Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing","Naturopathic","Yoga"],"location":"Kohala Coast","rating":5,"lat":19.818125,"lng":-155.833908,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Welcome to our Boutique Retreat Center on the Big Island of Hawaii.\n\nWe are currently on our own Sabbatical from retreats, trainings and classes.\n\nOur deepest gratitude to our guests and visitors who return to see us each year, however, \n\nwe will not be offering retreats in 2026. \n\nPlease contact us if you'd like to be notified of our future offerings in 2027. \n\nMahalo & Namaste,\n\nDan & Stacey","centerType":"retreat_center","centerTypeLabel":"Retreat Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"e3f75352-5667-4216-b85c-9c9ea93e7aef","name":"Hawaiian Sanctuary Retreat Center","image":"https://hawaiiansanctuary.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/x-accomodations-e1764366049514.webp","modality":"Yoga","modalities":["Yoga"],"location":"Pahoa","rating":5,"lat":19.482942,"lng":-154.941778,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"A Tropical Retreat Experience Accommodations, Eco Retreats, and Spa Facilities Hawaiian Sanctuary Retreat Center is an Eco Retreat nestled in the jungles of Big Island, Hawai’i. We are dedicated to providing accommodations, retreats, permaculture education as well as opportunities for personal and collective growth. We open our arms and our home to you with the...","centerType":"retreat_center","centerTypeLabel":"Retreat Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.