ent disco headphones. This is not just a yoga class, it’s an experience!","centerType":"yoga_studio","centerTypeLabel":"Yoga Studio","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":["https://www.yogabigisland.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/20220211_090810-scaled-e1677118672521.jpeg"],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"f1ebe1d8-a544-4c41-bf6b-9c889facef5c","name":"Yoga Centered","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/67d8ad108f62be5774970115/t/68003a967869c808d46e358e/1744845462759/1.jpg?format=1500w","modality":"Yoga","modalities":["Yoga"],"location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.726205,"lng":-155.087196,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"For over two decades, since 2002, we've nurtured a haven for those seeking to deepen their yoga practice and find mindful fitness. We welcome you to join our inclusive and ever-growing community, offering diverse classes (yoga, Pilates, Lagree, and more) and trainings for all levels!","centerType":"yoga_studio","centerTypeLabel":"Yoga Studio","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":["http://static1.squarespace.com/static/67d8ad108f62be5774970115/t/68003a967869c808d46e358e/1744845462759/1.jpg?format=1500w"],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"5d22b28d-39ac-4e52-b613-de1552895cbf","name":"Yoga Hale","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/1e0093_e63300b0dc534b32b1a7754dd23e4990~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_2200,h_634,al_c/1e0093_e63300b0dc534b32b1a7754dd23e4990~mv2.jpg","modality":"Somatic Therapy, Sound Healing, Yoga","modalities":["Somatic Therapy","Sound Healing","Yoga"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.59052,"lng":-155.969676,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"For over 20 years, Yoga Hale has been Kona’s trusted yoga studio on the Big Island of Hawaii, offering traditional and hot yoga just steps from Magic Sands Beach. We’re now expanding into wellness with new services including cryotherapy, lymphatic drainage, red light therapy, PEMF, and compression recovery — all focused on reducing pain, inflammation, and supporting true healing. Wellness isn’t a trend — it’s a lifestyle.","centerType":"yoga_studio","centerTypeLabel":"Yoga Studio","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":["https://static.wixstatic.com/media/1e0093_e63300b0dc534b32b1a7754dd23e4990~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_2200,h_634,al_c/1e0093_e63300b0dc534b32b1a7754dd23e4990~mv2.jpg"],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"3097bd45-b88f-4aa2-b0f9-590952614425","name":"Yoga Hawaii Bodhidevi","image":"http://www.bodhidevi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/fiorewatercolor-e1438900967501.png","modality":"Yoga, Nutrition, Fitness","modalities":["Yoga","Nutrition","Fitness"],"location":"Kealakekua","rating":5,"lat":19.503392,"lng":-155.925665,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"We are your ultimate healing resource. Bodhidevi provides innovative methods of yoga, nutrition, fitness, healing retreats, and lifestyle coaching.","centerType":"yoga_studio","centerTypeLabel":"Yoga Studio","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"37c1ee18-e992-4ab4-b09f-660ffca5aa52","name":"Yoga Oasis Hawaii","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/6876a23a0f9b0c1e5cc7b163/t/68cae6433b29f0613db63469/1761676705220/?format=1500w","modality":"Yoga","modalities":["Yoga"],"location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.723607,"lng":-155.084829,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"At Yoga Oasis Hawai’i, we honor the ancient wisdom of yoga with classes and \nworkshops that focus on more than just physical fitness. Rooted in 8-limb \nyogic philosophy, our studio’s holistic approach weaves traditional \npractices and mindful movement together, helping you navigate life’s waves \nwit","centerType":"yoga_studio","centerTypeLabel":"Yoga Studio","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"650a4e9a-5357-4c70-aa98-078b45328295","name":"You vs You Fitness","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/ff5782_b247cb2c54304806bdcc561f7130a4f8%7Emv2.jpg/v1/fit/w_2500,h_1330,al_c/ff5782_b247cb2c54304806bdcc561f7130a4f8%7Emv2.jpg","modality":"Yoga","modalities":["Yoga"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.643541,"lng":-155.994755,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Welcome to YOU vs YOU, where your fitness journey is about overcoming your biggest challenge: Yourself. We're not just about losing weight; we're about building a lifestyle that empowers you to be stronger, confident, and unstoppable.","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"bed21fc2-9b42-49f0-9d55-0d3588963af2","name":"Your Hawaiian Retreat","image":"","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Yoga","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Yoga"],"location":"Pahoa","rating":5,"lat":19.437802,"lng":-154.921783,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Your Hawaiian Retreat offers family vacation rentals, an organic retreat center for yoga practitioners, and a conference center for your business meetings on the Big Island.","centerType":"retreat_center","centerTypeLabel":"Retreat Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true}],"totalPractitioners":11,"totalCenters":51,"citiesServed":["Captain Cook","Hawi","Hilo","Holualoa","Honaunau-Napoopoo","Kailua-Kona","Kapaau","Keaau","Kealakekua","Kohala Coast","Paauhau","Pahoa","Volcano","Waikoloa","Waimea","big_island"]}]
